      <p>Sending warm wishes.  I always find in the tough moments life throws us, it&#39;s the simplest things that bring great joy.  Thank you for sharing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?p=666#comment-25827' data-commentid="25827" data-postid="666" data-belowelement="comment-25827" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-25828" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=666#comment-25828"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-12-20T04:03:02-05:00">Monday, December 20, 2010 at 4:03 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>A few years ago my 95 year old father-in-law was in a convalescent home after a stroke, when he came down with a fever &#8212; indicating pneumonia that we knew would be quickly fatal. He was immediately moved out of the room he shared with a minister to the private room next door.  My husband and I stayed with him that evening, and through the night.  During the evening, a group of friends visited the minister next door, and burst into gospel song; they serenaded us for over an hour with joyful music, and asked the nurse to tell us they were singing for us. I am quite sure it was the last sound that my father-in-law was aware of as he slipped into a coma a quietly died.  It was the most beautiful expression of pure love I have ever experienced, and I bless those lovely people every time I recall that night.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?p=666#comment-25828' data-commentid="25828" data-postid="666" data-belowelement="comment-25828" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
